This paper deals with Natural Language Sentence Matching (NLSM) datasets and proposes a framework to alleviate selection bias. This topic falls under the sub-category of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also discusses machine learning techniques and evaluation results, which are relevant to sub-categories such as Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), and Computer Vision (cs.CV).
